---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Services" description="Workflow automation, custom AI agents, integrations, and internal tools for small businesses.">
  <section class="py-20">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h1 class="font-display text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-stone-900 text-center mb-6">
        Services
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-stone-600 text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-16">
        Everything I build is designed to run reliably, document itself, and save you real time.
      </p>
      
      <!-- Workflow Automation -->
      <div id="automation" class="mb-20 scroll-mt-32">
        <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-start">
          <div>
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-amber-100 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-amber-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 4v5h.582m15.356 2A8.001 8.001 0 004.582 9m0 0H9m11 11v-5h-.581m0 0a8.003 8.003 0 01-15.357-2m15.357 2H15"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h2 class="font-display text-3xl font-bold text-stone-900 mb-4">Workflow Automation</h2>
            <p class="text-stone-600 text-lg mb-6">
              Connect your apps and eliminate manual data entry. I build automations using Zapier, Make, n8n, or custom scripts—whatever fits your needs and budget.
            </p>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-stone-900 mb-3">Common builds:</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-stone-600">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-copper shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                </svg>
                Lead capture → CRM sync → follow-up sequences
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-copper shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                </svg>
                Order received → inventory update → shipping notification
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-copper shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                </svg>
                Invoice paid → update spreadsheet → notify bookkeeper
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-copper shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                </svg>
                Scheduled data pulls → report generation → email delivery
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-stone-200 p-8">
            <h4 class="text-sm uppercase tracking-wide text-stone-400 mb-4">What you get</h4>
            <ul class="space-y-4">
              <li class="flex gap-4">
                <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-stone-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 text-stone-600 font-semibold">1</div>
                <div>
                  <span class="font-semibold text-stone-900">Working automation</span>
                  <p class="text-stone-600 text-sm mt-1">Tested, deployed, and running in production</p>
                </div>
              </li>
              <li class="flex gap-4">
                <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-stone-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 text-stone-600 font-semibold">2</div>
                <div>
                  <span class="font-semibold text-stone-900">Error handling</span>
                  <p class="text-stone-600 text-sm mt-1">Graceful failures with alerts, not silent breakage</p>
                </div>
              </li>
              <li class="flex gap-4">
                <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-stone-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 text-stone-600 font-semibold">3</div>
                <div>
                  <span class="font-semibold text-stone-900">Documentation</span>
                  <p class="text-stone-600 text-sm mt-1">Written guide so anyone can understand what it does</p>
                </div>
              </li>
              <li class="flex gap-4">
                <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-stone-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 text-stone-600 font-semibold">4</div>
                <div>
                  <span class="font-semibold text-stone-900">Logging</span>
                  <p class="text-stone-600 text-sm mt-1">Audit trail so you can see what happened and when</p>
                </div>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- AI Agents -->
      <div id="agents" class="mb-20 scroll-mt-32">
        <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-start">
          <div class="lg:order-2">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-blue-100 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-blue-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h2 class="font-display text-3xl font-bold text-stone-900 mb-4">Custom AI Agents</h2>
            <p class="text-stone-600 text-lg mb-6">
              AI that does actual work—not just chat. I build agents using Claude, GPT-4, or local models that can read, classify, draft, and take action on your behalf.
            </p>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-stone-900 mb-3">Common builds:</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-stone-600">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-copper shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                </svg>
                Email triage: classify, route, draft responses
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-copper shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                </svg>
                Document processing: extract data from invoices, contracts, forms
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-copper shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                </svg>
                Knowledge assistants: answer questions from your docs/SOPs
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-copper shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                </svg>
                Report generators: summarize data into human-readable updates
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-stone-200 p-8 lg:order-1">
            <h4 class="text-sm uppercase tracking-wide text-stone-400 mb-4">What makes it reliable</h4>
            <ul class="space-y-4">
              <li class="flex gap-4">
                <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-blue-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
                  <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-blue-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"></path>
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <span class="font-semibold text-stone-900">Guardrails</span>
                  <p class="text-stone-600 text-sm mt-1">Limits on what the AI can do—no runaway actions</p>
                </div>
              </li>
              <li class="flex gap-4">
                <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-blue-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
                  <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-blue-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2M9 5a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2M9 5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2m-6 9l2 2 4-4"></path>
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <span class="font-semibold text-stone-900">Evaluation</span>
                  <p class="text-stone-600 text-sm mt-1">Test cases that verify the AI behaves correctly</p>
                </div>
              </li>
              <li class="flex gap-4">
                <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-blue-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
                  <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-blue-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 12a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"></path>
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M2.458 12C3.732 7.943 7.523 5 12 5c4.478 0 8.268 2.943 9.542 7-1.274 4.057-5.064 7-9.542 7-4.477 0-8.268-2.943-9.542-7z"></path>
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <span class="font-semibold text-stone-900">Human oversight</span>
                  <p class="text-stone-600 text-sm mt-1">Option for human review before critical actions</p>
                </div>
              </li>
              <li class="flex gap-4">
                <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-blue-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
                  <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-blue-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z"></path>
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <span class="font-semibold text-stone-900">Monitoring</span>
                  <p class="text-stone-600 text-sm mt-1">Track performance and catch issues early</p>
                </div>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Integrations -->
      <div id="integrations" class="mb-20 scroll-mt-32">
        <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-start">
          <div>
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-green-100 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-green-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13.828 10.172a4 4 0 00-5.656 0l-4 4a4 4 0 105.656 5.656l1.102-1.101m-.758-4.899a4 4 0 005.656 0l4-4a4 4 0 00-5.656-5.656l-1.1 1.1"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h2 class="font-display text-3xl font-bold text-stone-900 mb-4">Integrations</h2>
            <p class="text-stone-600 text-lg mb-6">
              Make your tools talk to each other. I connect APIs, webhooks, and databases so data flows automatically without manual intervention.
            </p>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-stone-900 mb-3">Tools I work with:</h3>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 text-sm">
              <span class="bg-stone-100 text-stone-700 px-3 py-1 rounded-full">HubSpot</span>
              <span class="bg-stone-100 text-stone-700 px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Salesforce</span>
              <span class="bg-stone-100 text-stone-700 px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Airtable</span>
              <span class="bg-stone-100 text-stone-700 px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Google Sheets</span>
              <span class="bg-stone-100 text-stone-700 px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Notion</span>
              <span class="bg-stone-100 text-stone-700 px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Slack</span>
              <span class="bg-stone-100 text-stone-700 px-3 py-1 rounded-full">QuickBooks</span>
              <span class="bg-stone-100 text-stone-700 px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Stripe</span>
              <span class="bg-stone-100 text-stone-700 px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Shopify</span>
              <span class="bg-stone-100 text-stone-700 px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Twilio</span>
              <span class="bg-stone-100 text-stone-700 px-3 py-1 rounded-full">SendGrid</span>
              <span class="bg-stone-100 text-stone-700 px-3 py-1 rounded-full">PostgreSQL</span>
              <span class="bg-stone-100 text-stone-700 px-3 py-1 rounded-full">REST APIs</span>
              <span class="bg-stone-100 text-stone-700 px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Webhooks</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-stone-500 text-sm mt-4">+ most tools with API or export capabilities</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-stone-900 rounded-2xl p-8 text-stone-50">
            <h4 class="font-semibold mb-4">No API? No problem.</h4>
            <p class="text-stone-300 mb-6">
              If your tool only exports CSV or Excel, I can still automate around it using file watchers, email parsing, or scheduled imports. The goal is to eliminate manual work—I'll find a way.
            </p>
            <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center text-copper hover:underline">
              Ask about your specific tools
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 ml-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"></path>
              </svg>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Internal Tools & Reliability -->
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div id="tools" class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-stone-200 p-8 scroll-mt-32">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-purple-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-purple-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 5a1 1 0 011-1h14a1 1 0 011 1v2a1 1 0 01-1 1H5a1 1 0 01-1-1V5zM4 13a1 1 0 011-1h6a1 1 0 011 1v6a1 1 0 01-1 1H5a1 1 0 01-1-1v-6zM16 13a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v6a1 1 0 01-1 1h-2a1 1 0 01-1-1v-6z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold text-stone-900 mb-3">Internal Tools</h3>
          <p class="text-stone-600 mb-4">
            Lightweight dashboards and admin panels that give your team visibility without the overhead of complex software.
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-stone-600 text-sm">
            <li>• Status dashboards for key metrics</li>
            <li>• Admin panels for managing data</li>
            <li>• Simple CRUD apps for internal processes</li>
            <li>• Reporting views that update automatically</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        
        <div id="reliability" class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-stone-200 p-8 scroll-mt-32">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-red-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-red-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold text-stone-900 mb-3">Reliability Layer</h3>
          <p class="text-stone-600 mb-4">
            The unsexy stuff that keeps everything running. Included in every project because automation without reliability is just a different kind of problem.
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-stone-600 text-sm">
            <li>• Comprehensive logging</li>
            <li>• Retry logic for transient failures</li>
            <li>• Alert notifications when things go wrong</li>
            <li>• Version control and rollback capability</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-stone-900 text-stone-50">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
      <h2 class="font-display text-3xl font-bold mb-6">
        Ready to automate?
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-stone-400 mb-8">
        Tell me what's eating up your time. I'll tell you what we can fix.
      </p>
      <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-copper text-stone-50 px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-semibold text-lg hover:opacity-90 transition-opacity">
        Book a free consultation
        <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"></path>
        </svg>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
